@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-governance#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-governance>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Governance & Finality" ;
  rdfs:comment "PoA/PoR consensus, identity crystals, program charters, CTQs." .

### Identity & non-transferability
:IdentityCrystal a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf bs:Crystal .
:transferable a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :IdentityCrystal ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:boundToEntity a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :IdentityCrystal ; rdfs:range rdfs:Resource .

### Validators & consensus mechanisms
:Validator a owl:Class .
:ProofOfAgreement a owl:Class .
:ProofOfReputation a owl:Class .

:approves a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Validator ; rdfs:range bs:Crystal .
:weight a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Validator ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .
:reputation a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Validator ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .

### Consensus thresholds
:quorum a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :ProofOfAgreement ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .
:weightThreshold a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :ProofOfReputation ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .

### Program governance
:ProgramCharter a owl:Class .
:CTQ a owl:Class .
:tracksCTQ a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :ProgramCharter ; rdfs:range :CTQ .
:enforces a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:ByteEthos ; rdfs:range :ProgramCharter .

### Finality mechanisms
:finalizes a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:ByteEthos ; rdfs:range bs:LedgerSegment .
:consensusReached a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:LedgerSegment ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:finalityHeight a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:LedgerSegment ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .